text: Avdotyino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Aksinyinskoye Rural Settlement of Aksinyinskoye Rural Settlement, Stupinsky District, Moscow Oblast, Russia. The population was 75 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == The khutor is located between rivers Kononkova and Severka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Moscow Oblast
title: Avdotyino, Aksinyinskoye Rural Settlement, Stupinsky District, Moscow Oblast
